<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/images/witechlogo.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/departmentform.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Outreach and Public Relations</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-12 volunteer-box">
                        <div class="form-box"> 
                            <h2 class=>Outreach and Public Relations Head Form</h2>
                            <form action="#" onsubmit="submitForm('out-pr-hd-opr');return false;">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mName">Full Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="mName"  id="mName" placeholder="Name" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mMail">E-Mail</label>
                                    <input type="email" name="mMail"  id="mMail" placeholder="E-mail" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>                            
                                
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mContact">Contact</label>
                                    <input type="text" minlength="10" maxlength="10" name="mContact" id="mContact" placeholder="Contact" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="education">Educational Details</label>
                                    <textarea name="education" class="form-control" cols="20" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="cv">CV (Google Docs Link)</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="cv"  id="" placeholder="C.V Link" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question1">As an Outreach and PR head how do you think you can contribute to the team?</label>
                                    <textarea name="question1" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question2">Do you have any prior experience in leadership and handling teams? </label>
                                    <textarea name="question2" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question3"> Task:An employee of a reputed XYZ company was fired from the company for malpractices.The malpractice being the employee leaking important information to the rival company.
                                        Upon losing his job he retaliates by tweeting where he criticizes in order to defame the company.The tweets blow up and the public starts detesting the company.
                                        The sponsored chief guest speaker for the upcoming event calls you to inform his withdrawal from the event due to the negative reaction which may lead to cancellation of the entire event.</label>
                                        <p style="margin: 0%;">1.As an Outreach and public realtion head how will you deal with the crisis and gain back the trust of the public?</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0%;">2.How will you convince the speaker to join the event?</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0%;">3.What directions will you give to your team of 4 i.e event planner, event coordinator, outreach & partnership specialist, and community builder to solve the problem?</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0%;">Eludicate your views and entail various strategies to answer the given questions in atleast 100 words</p>
                                    <textarea name="question3" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>


                                <div class="button-row">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                                </div>
                                <div id="formalert"></div>
                            </form>

                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 
    <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script> 
    <script src="/javascript/departmentform.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
